<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Sephcocco</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .welcome-message {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #27ae60;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #7f8c8d;
      border-top: 1px solid #ecf0f1;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">Sephcocco</div>
      <div class="welcome-message">Welcome to Sephcocco!</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</p>
      
      <p>Welcome to Sephcocco! We're excited to have you join our community. Your account has been successfully created.</p>
      
      <p>With your Sephcocco account, you can:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Browse and order from our lounge, restaurant, and pharmacy</li>
        <li>Track your orders in real-time</li>
        <li>Manage your profile and preferences</li>
        <li>Receive updates on new products and promotions</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>To get started, please confirm your email address by clicking the confirmation link we've sent to you separately.</p>
      
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for choosing Sephcocco!</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>
      The Sephcocco Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to <%= @user.email %>. If you didn't create an account with Sephcocco, please ignore this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= Date.current.year %> Sephcocco. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
